achena prem is a 2011 bengali film directed by swapan saha and produced under the banner of maa kali films . the movie is an unofficial remake of hit kannada movie mussanjemaatu.surprisingly the fact that it is a remake of the kannada movie has not been mentioned either on the achena prem 's official website or in other reviews/articles on the internet 2 kannada songs from the original have been also retained in the movie . the song " kar mone te ki swopno thake " is the bengali version of kannada song " enagali munde saagu nee " and " tomake bhebe mon " is the bengali version of kannada song " ninna nodalento " .